column3: “got a great high from this strain: talkative, happy, no paranoia or anxiety at all”
“One of my favorites for relaxing in the evening. Let's the tension from the day melt away and quiets the stress in the head.”

“small buds at first but pheno 3 is a unique strain tha when grown useing mills with sugaree and full power its a one of a kind strain that looks SC l I e no other strain i ever seen looks like knots”
“VERY FRUITY SMELL. TASTE GOOD. NICE DAYTIME HIGH. STARTED FROM SEEDS.. EASY TO GROW.”

“This is a mother of all strains. You can smoke this and take all your pain away and be uplifted and want to take on a project that you have been putting off because your nervous and let's you be the true you behind the shell. I also noticed it has helped me clear my head and take away the pressure to have a clear true cognitive state.”
“very fruity smell with tons of crystals”
“Easy strain to grow with giant buds that have a nice, sweet smell. Extremely sticky and resinous. Great for concentrates.”
“I feel very chatty and happy with this train, its good to chill with, very light and flowy feeling.”

“Im not a fan of this strain at all and quite annoyed that i paid 20 for a preroll of miss USA from an employee at Pisos in las vegas and said it would help me feel relaxed and go to sleep cause i have anxiety well i def didnt feel tired i couldnt sleep all night and the high made me irritated the last strain i bought was blueberry and was perfect but they were out of that one so make sure you do your research before ...”
